Name: Pretty Girls Mahjong Solitaire [GREEN]
About the game: The Pretty Girls are back again with a new version!! Enjoy this newest installment in the Pretty Girls Mahjong Solitaire universe! Let's go GREEN and get back to nature! This time all of the anime girls have animal features. How exciting! Clear the tiles to reveal their sexy costumes. Do you have what it takes to clear all the tiles for more Pretty Girl surprises?! ■ Classic Mahjong Solitaire rules Find pairs of tiles to delete them. Delete all tiles before time runs out to clear a round. Think strategically when deleting tiles, or you might run into a dead end! Adding over 60 patterns of tiles. The tiles get shuffled every time you play, making it fun to play again and again. ■ Pretty Girls are waiting for you to come play! Five characters appear in this game. Once you make it to the third round, a girl in a sexy costume begins to reveal herself as you delete tiles... As you clear stages, the girls get sexier and sexier! All characters have recorded voices! ■ Character Introductions PRIMINA The daughter of a dog-human mother, she has pleasant features with an easy going and obedient personality. SUMIRE A youkai, animal spirit in human form. She's a fox spirit with a devious mind but also a gentle older sister. SHERIRA A cat-girl with strong features and a powerful, tsundere personality. NAZUNA A racoon spirit in human form, she has a quiet personality and lives life at her own pace. LATY She's a dog-girl with a friendly personality that matches her soft and fluffy features. ※This is a puzzle game with sexy characters (no nudity).
